    public static final String CONST_OM_FAQ_CONTENT2 ="MANTRA Chain is a vertically-integrated enterprise network for Web3. Built on Cosmos SDK, MANTRA Chain is interoperable with other blockchains in Cosmos with the IBC module and provides fertile ground and developer tools to build anything from NFTs, games, and virtual universes to secure and compliant decentralized exchanges. The blockchain is also EVM compatible bringing the flexibility and reliability of both the Cosmos and Ethereum ecosystems together in a builder friendly environment.";
    public static final String CONST_OM_FAQ_CONTENT3 ="MANTRA involves its community at every stage, and the transparent governance mechanism is the core that brings the people together. To reach a wider community outside of the OMniverse and Sherpas, MANTRA DAO strives to bring this narrative and structure to other projects and their many protocols.  MANTRA DAO offers a range of DAO services that securely increase efficiencies of various DAOs’ business functions ranging from finance to human resources management. DAO solutions include treasury management, DAO issuance & launchpads, DAO governance & grants as well as DAO staking and DeFi.";

